channel.title: Looking for server team!
channel.description:
Hi everyone,
I'm starting a new server and I'm looking for a team to support me (a development team)
I'd like to have following members in my team: -a programmer (java :)) -somebody that can desin (and menage) the site and/or forums -a serverhost (can be owner if he/she wants) -... (if you have an other suggestion then let me know ;))
Ow and I can code java (but not good so I can help but I'm not planning to do very mush java coding),vb (I menage vb good ,I'm not an expert but not a newby either) (I can code restarter and stuf like that)
what source our server will be running will be decided later (together whit some of the team members).(so if you report soon enough you can help us chose that and some other things)
If your interested just post it here or pm me.
I hope a lot of people respond :D (ow and if this is posted at the wrong place please move it)
